headline: Altria’s 6.5% Dividend Has Been Raised For 20 Years, But Will it Continue?
summary: Altria Group Inc (NYSE:MO) is the company behind Marlboro cigarettes and smokeless tobacco products. It delivers one of Wall Street’s highest dividend yields at 6.36%. For retirees hunting income, that yield is hard to ignore. The question is whether it’s built on solid foundation or borrowed time. The company pays $1.06 per share quarterly, annualizing ...
